【Multiple Usage Scenarios】The simple and fashionable exterior design complements various home styles, making your 5 tier bookshelf not only a place to store, but also a decoration, adding an artistic atmosphere to your space. Perfectly fit with living room, bedroom, study, entrance, hallway, office, etc.

【Waterproof & Anti-scratch】Our bookshelf panels with top notch waterproof coating and anti-scratch features are very easy to clean. The metal frame combined with thick board brings strong weight capacity to hold your heavy items without wobbling.

【Anti-tip Kits & Easy Assembly】The beautiful bookcase comes with an anti-tipping tool, please mount this tool on the wall for better stability and less unexpected injuries. You can easily complete the installation of the 5 shelf bookcase according to the installation video we provide. Quick and easy to assemble, so you can enjoy the convenience of your new bookshelf immediately.

reviews.reviewText: First of all it did not have directions. I should have stopped putting it together after a few of the holes were not lining up correctly. Not very sturdy, none of the holes lined up, had to drill holes to assemble it, some of the shelves had holes but they were so close to the edge that they blew the sides out of the shelf, we had to go buy hardware cause it did not have enough. I give lightweight 3 stars cause it is very light. The shelves are not 13" apart they are about 10-11" at most, they also do not hold more than 15 lbs. I called to see if Amazon would compensate me for at least the hardware and they will not. DO NOT BUY!!!!!

reviews.reviewText: Took a while for the color I wanted to be shipped but for the price I love it. I compared a lot and took a chance since none of the reviews were for this tower shelf. Looks like any other "expensive" shelving unit I've bought. Everything was labeled properly, even the hardware was numbered in their own section bags. Would definitely buy again from this seller. Only flaw was one of the screws were stripped and the seller didn't put an extra one in of that screw. I'm using mine for the rest of my shoes and purses since I have so many.Update: bought another one lol, this one I'm going to use to organize all my wallets and clutches.

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Attractive and versatile!
reviews.reviewText: I was looking for a good shelf for my dolls and home decor, and I'm glad I chose this one!Putting it together was a breeze. The assembly process was straightforward, and the instructions were easy to follow. I appreciated that I didn't need a toolbox full of tools – everything required was included. Within no time, I had a sturdy and functional shelf ready to use.The classic modern design is something I particularly love. It seamlessly fits into any room, giving it a touch of sophistication. The neutral look makes it versatile, and I can see it complementing various decor styles.In terms of sturdiness, it doesn't disappoint. The shelves are well-supported, and I feel confident placing a variety of books and other items on them. It's become a reliable storage solution for my collection.Overall, this shelf is a winner for me. Easy assembly, sturdy construction, and a design that suits any room – what more could you ask for in a shelf? If you're in need of a practical and stylish storage solution, this one is definitely worth considering!
